  <summary>A simple Flatpak store</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
    It will help you install Flatpak apps in a user-friendly way. We have recipes for some of them to install them even better. 
    </p>
    <p>
    For example, for Steam, it asks the user to choose a folder where they store their games before installation.
    </p>
    <p>Available in language EN / ES / FR / IT</p>
  </description>

